      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Taijutsu (Strike)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 7 (Spell Level 4)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 7</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 21 | <b>Successes:</b> 4</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 9 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 22</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> Mob</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>Make a Full Attack with your bone weapon against the target, gaining an additional attack at your highest attack bonus -5. For 1 round after the attacks, you gain a +1 bonus to Reflex saves, and a +1 dodge bonus to Defense.</p>\n\n\n\n",
